<h2 id="account-security-features">Account Security Features</h2>

<h3 id="multi-factor-authentication">Multi Factor Authentication</h3>
<p>In our GUI, we make sure that your account is always secure, thatâ€™s why we supported a Time-Based One Time Password (TOTP) as a second authentication mechanism.<br />
To activate it, all you have to do is to follow the simple steps listed in the MFA activation page.</p>

<image src="/docs/images/screenshots/mfa.png" width="500" />

<p><br /></p>

<h3 id="change-password">Change password</h3>
<p>Changing your password regularly reduces your risk of exposure and avoids a number of dangers. Thatâ€™s wahy we supported the <strong>Change Password</strong> in our GUI.</p>

<image src="/docs/images/screenshots/change-password.png" width="500" />

<p><br /></p>

<h3 id="session-timeout">Session Timeout</h3>
<p>This is another security mechanism we support in our GUI: Session Timeout! <br />
Your login session is valid for only 30 min, after this you will get logged out automatically.</p>
<image src="/docs/images/screenshots/session-timeout.png" width="400" />

